        "synopsis": {
            "value": "Professional billiards player Yin Guo eagerly accepts an invitation to a tournament in Hel, unaware that a snowstorm will leave her stranded with Lin Yi Yang. An instant connection forms between them, and as they get to know each other, Yin Guo learns that Yi Yang was once a billiards genius who faded from the spotlight. Inspired by Yin Guo's passion for the sport, Yi Yang decides to make a comeback to\n\nprofessional billiards.",
